SSPL AV Plugin test types:
https://wiki.sophos.net/display/SAVLU/SSPL+AV+Plugin+Test+types

Automated Test Standards & Behaviors:
https://wiki.sophos.net/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=317105394

How we can use TAP spike:
https://wiki.sophos.net/display/LD/How+we+can+use+TAP+spike

How to: Set up and Use TAP in SSPL-AV:
https://wiki.sophos.net/display/SAVLU/How+to%3A+Set+up+and+Use+TAP+in+SSPL-AV

In order to run these tests in TAP do:
 1) activate the tap environment:
    source tapvenv/bin/activate
 2) tap run av_plugin.integration --debug-loop for integration tests
    tap run av_plugin.component --debug-loop for component tests
    tap run av_plugin.coverage for coverage tests

In order to run them in Vagrant box:
    vagrant up
    vagrant ssh
    sudo mkdir -p /opt/test/inputs
    sudo mkdir -p /opt/test/inputs/av/
    sudo ln -s /vagrant/sspl-plugin-anti-virus/TA/ /opt/test/inputs/test_scripts
    sudo ln -s /vagrant/sspl-plugin-anti-virus/output/SDDS-COMPONENT /opt/test/inputs/av/SDDS-COMPONENT
    sudo ln -s /vagrant/sspl-plugin-anti-virus/output/test-resources /opt/test/inputs/av/test-resources
    sudo ln -s /vagrant/sspl-plugin-anti-virus/output/base-sdds /opt/test/inputs/av/base-sdds
    sudo apt-get -y install python3.7 python3.7-dev python3-pip zip
    sudo -H python3.7 -m pip install pyzmq protobuf pytest-html robotframework Cython pycapnp
    cd /vagrant/sspl-plugin-anti-virus/TA
    sudo python3.7 -m robot .

To run a single test:
    sudo python3.7 -m robot --test "<name>" --removekeywords WUKS  .lib

To run specific suites:
    sudo python3.7 -m robot -s TA.Product.AVCommandLineScanner .
    sudo python3.7 -m robot -s TA.Product.AvBasic .
    sudo python3.7 -m robot -s TA.Integration.AvAndBase .

To run a full set of tests similar to TAP:
    python3 -m robot --include "INTEGRATION OR PRODUCT" --exclude "OSTIA OR MANUAL OR STRESS" --removekeywords WUKS  .

